This is a poker game where{nl}
you can exchange cards once.{waitkey}{clearbox}First, five cards are{nl}
dealt to you.{waitkey}{clearbox}Use the directional buttons{nl}
to select cards to keep,{waitkey}{nl}
then press O/X/Triangle/Square{nl}
to HOLD them.{waitkey}{clearbox}Once you've decided which{nl}
cards to hold, press R1 or R2{nl}
to perform a REDRAW,{waitkey}{nl}
replacing the unheld cards.{waitkey}{clearbox}After the redraw, if you{nl}
have a winning hand,{nl}
you win!{waitkey}{clearbox}The more coins you bet,{nl}
the higher the payout (ODDS){nl}
when you complete a hand.{waitkey}{clearbox}When you complete a hand,{nl}
you can challenge an EXTRA{nl}
GAME wagering your payout.{waitkey}{clearbox}If you don't want to play{nl}
the Extra Game, select{nl}
TAKE SCORE.{waitkey}{clearbox}There are 3 types of{nl}
Extra Games. In each,{nl}
your payout doubles per win.{waitkey}{clearbox}By winning consecutively,{nl}
the Extra Game payout can{nl}
reach up to 1,000,000 coins.{waitkey}{clearbox}But if you lose even once,{nl}
all coins at stake are{nl}
forfeited, so be careful.{waitkey}{clearbox}<Extra Game 1>{nl}
- HI & LOW{waitkey}{clearbox}One face-up card and four{nl}
face-down cards are{nl}
shown on screen.{waitkey}{clearbox}Pick the one face-down card{nl}
whose value is higher than{nl}
the face-up card.{waitkey}{clearbox}If the chosen card matches{nl}
the face-up card's value,{nl}
it's a draw — try again.{waitkey}{clearbox}<Extra Game 2>{nl}
- BIG & SMALL{waitkey}{clearbox}One face-up card and one{nl}
face-down card are{nl}
shown on screen.{waitkey}{clearbox}Guess whether the face-down{nl}
card is higher or lower{nl}
than the face-up card.{waitkey}{clearbox}If the two cards match,{nl}
you lose — so be careful.{waitkey}{clearbox}<Extra Game 3>{nl}
- RED & BLACK{waitkey}{clearbox}One face-down card is{nl}
shown on screen.{waitkey}{clearbox}If you think the face-down{nl}
card is a Heart or Diamond,{nl}
choose "RED".{waitkey}{clearbox}If you think it is a Spade{nl}
or Club, choose "BLACK".{waitkey}{clearbox}If your chosen color matches{nl}
the card's color, you win.{waitkey}{ret}

