WIN:{nl}
The player's total doesn't{nl}
exceed 21{waitkey}{nl}
and is higher than the{nl}
dealer's, or the dealer{nl}
BUSTs.{waitkey}{clearbox}B. JACK:{nl}
(BLACK JACK){nl}
An Ace plus any 10-K card.{waitkey}{nl}
(STAND is automatic.){nl}
After a SPLIT, this counts{nl}
as 21 instead.{waitkey}{clearbox}6 CARDS:{nl}
6 cards drawn without{nl}
exceeding 21,{waitkey}{nl}
then the player STANDs.{waitkey}{clearbox}7 CARDS:{nl}
7 cards drawn without{nl}
exceeding 21.{waitkey}{nl}
(STAND is automatic.){waitkey}{clearbox}Heart/Club/Diamond A & J:{nl}
A Blackjack with Ace and{nl}
Jack, both cards being{waitkey}{nl}
Hearts, Clubs, or{nl}
Diamonds.{waitkey}{clearbox}Spade A & J:{nl}
A Blackjack with Ace and{nl}
Jack, both cards being{waitkey}{nl}
Spades.{waitkey}{clearbox}777:{nl}
Both dealt cards are 7s,{nl}
and the third HIT card{waitkey}{nl}
is also a 7.{waitkey}{ret}

