{ctl0e:6}{ret}

This slot machine consists{nl}
of 5 large drums and{nl}
16 small drums.{waitkey}{clearbox}The number of coins you bet{nl}
increases the number of{nl}
active lines.{waitkey}{clearbox}You can bet up to{nl}
8 coins.{waitkey}{clearbox}Bets 1, 2, 5, 6: horizontal{nl}
lines. Bets 3, 4, 7, 8:{nl}
vertical lines.{waitkey}{clearbox}Bets 5-8 each have{nl}
2 lines per{nl}
bet.{waitkey}{clearbox}When the game starts, all{nl}
large and small drums{nl}
begin spinning.{waitkey}{clearbox}After spinning a while, the{nl}
small drums stop first.{nl}
(The large drum keeps going.){waitkey}{clearbox}Press O/X/Triangle/Square to{nl}
shift the small drums{nl}
clockwise.{waitkey}{clearbox}Adjust the small drums to{nl}
make matching symbols{nl}
easier to line up.{waitkey}{clearbox}Once you've adjusted the{nl}
small drums, press R1 or R2{nl}
to stop the large drum.{waitkey}{clearbox}If 3 or more of the same{nl}
symbol appear in a row on{nl}
your active lines, you win.{waitkey}{clearbox}Bets 1-4: up to 5 in a row.{nl}
Bets 5-8: up to 4 in a row.{waitkey}{clearbox}Also, if the large drum's{nl}
symbols align diagonally,{nl}
in the 4 corners, or all,{waitkey}{nl}
you win regardless of{nl}
your active bet lines.{waitkey}{clearbox}Wins on the large drum{nl}
multiply the payout{nl}
by the number of coins bet.{waitkey}{ret}

