Each slot machine has{nl}
different symbols that are{nl}
easier to hit.{waitkey}{clearbox}Rather than sticking to one{nl}
machine, try out different{nl}
ones.{waitkey}{clearbox}During the game, it's easy{nl}
to forget to adjust the{nl}
small drums — be careful.{waitkey}{nl}
Adjusting them well is the{nl}
secret to increasing your{nl}
coin count.{waitkey}{clearbox}Betting small amounts is{nl}
risky when it counts most.{waitkey}{nl}
It's best to always bet{nl}
the max (8 BET).{waitkey}{ret}

