Two dice are rolled on{nl}
screen. Guess the total.{waitkey}{clearbox}There are 11 spots to bet{nl}
on (totals 2-12). You may{nl}
bet on multiple spots,{waitkey}{nl}
but max 100 per spot.{waitkey}{clearbox}If you bet on the correct{nl}
total, you win and receive{nl}
the payout for that total.{waitkey}{clearbox}When you win, you can{nl}
also wager your payout{nl}
on an Extra Game.{waitkey}{clearbox}The Extra Game is not about{nl}
guessing the exact total.{waitkey}{nl}
Instead, any total other{nl}
than 7 is a win.{waitkey}{nl}
(Payouts vary by total.){waitkey}{nl}
But if a 7 is rolled,{nl}
the game ends and all{nl}
coins at stake are lost.{waitkey}{ret}

