In this game, totals closer{nl}
to 7 have lower payouts,{nl}
and come up more often.{waitkey}{clearbox}So it's wise to bet more{nl}
on totals near 7, and{nl}
less on totals near 2 or 12.{waitkey}{clearbox}In the Extra Game, if a 7{nl}
rolls, all your earned coins{nl}
are forfeited.{waitkey}{nl}
The trick is to not get{nl}
greedy and stop at a{nl}
reasonable point.{waitkey}{ret}

