The key in this game is to{nl}
find squares that are a HIT{nl}
in both their row and column.{waitkey}{clearbox}Once you find such a square,{nl}
mark it for reference.{waitkey}{clearbox}Also, the RESULT display{nl}
showing your past inputs is{nl}
a big hint — use it well.{waitkey}{ret}
